'''额上回'''（{{lang-en|Superior frontal gyrus}}）是[[大脑|大脑]][[额叶|额叶]]的一个[[脑回|脑回]]，占据额叶大小的三分之一。<ref>{{Cite web|title=额上回|url=https://www.imaios.com/cn/e-Anatomy/node_322323/2734|accessdate=2021-04-09|work=IMAIOS|language=zh}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Superior Frontal Gyrus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/superior-frontal-gyrus|accessdate=2021-04-09|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en}}</ref> 额上回下方与[[额上沟|额上沟]]相连，而额上回延伸至[[大脑半球|大脑半球]]内侧的部分称为[[额内回|额内回]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=BrainInfo|url=http://braininfo.rprc.washington.edu/centraldirectory.aspx?ID=83|accessdate=2021-04-09|work=|publisher=[[华盛顿大学|华盛顿大学]]|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":02">{{Cite web|title=Medial frontal gyrus|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/medial-frontal-gyrus?lang=us#:~:text=The%20medial%20frontal%20gyrus%20is,contains%20the%20supplementary%20motor%20area.|accessdate=2021-04-09|last=Gaillard|first=Frank|work=|publisher=Radiopaedia|language=en-US}}</ref>

== 功能 ==
额上回参与脑部的高阶认知功能，尤其是[[工作记忆|工作记忆]]。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Functions of the left superior frontal gyrus in humans: a lesion study|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16984899/|last=du Boisgueheneuc|first=Foucaud|last2=Levy|first2=Richard|date=2006-12|journal=Brain: A Journal of Neurology|issue=Pt 12|doi=10.1093/brain/awl244|volume=129|pages=3315–3328|issn=1460-2156|pmid=16984899|last3=Volle|first3=Emmanuelle|last4=Seassau|first4=Magali|last5=Duffau|first5=Hughes|last6=Kinkingnehun|first6=Serge|last7=Samson|first7=Yves|last8=Zhang|first8=Sandy|last9=Dubois|first9=Bruno}}</ref> [[大脑半球|大脑半球]]一侧的额上回负责规划身体另一侧的部分复杂运动。<ref name=":0" />

一些[[功能性磁共振成像|功能性磁共振成像]]实验显示，额上回与[[自我意识|自我意识]]有关。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=When the Brain Loses Its Self: Prefrontal Inactivation during Sensorimotor Processing|url=https://www.cell.com/neuron/abstract/S0896-6273(06)00212-1|last=Goldberg|first=Ilan I.|last2=Harel|first2=Michal|date=2006-04-20|journal=Neuron|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.neuron.2006.03.015|volume=50|pages=329–339|language=en|issn=0896-6273|pmid=16630842|last3=Malach|first3=Rafael}}</ref> 此外，也有实验显示，额上回与人的[[笑|笑]]有关联。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Electric current stimulates laughter|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/35536|last=Fried|first=Itzhak|last2=Wilson|first2=Charles L.|date=1998-02-XX|journal=Nature|issue=6668|doi=10.1038/35536|volume=391|pages=650–650|language=en|issn=1476-4687|last3=MacDonald|first3=Katherine A.|last4=Behnke|first4=Eric J.}}</ref>

